headline: Feeling charitable? GoFundMe creates a new way to give money.
summary: GoFundMe launched a new platform for charitable giving called Giving Funds, which lets you create your own donor-advised fund for making donations to 501(c)(3) nonprofits.

headline: ‘We Expect Bitcoin to Top $200K by the End of Year’, Says Bitwise CIO
summary: With the bitcoin price reaching a new all-time high earlier this week, crypto industry leaders and analysts are starting to expect a lot more from BTC in 2025.
